{"tid":87072,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Kodi/XBMC 集中討論區(1) 免費劇集任睇，跨平台支援","createTime":"2017-01-19T14:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T13:52:49.000Z","uid":77675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b49b355772aef0db97e34639d617be88366279fc","tid":87072,"uid":77675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"Kodi是由XBMC基金會開發的開源媒體播放器，原名XBMC。<br />\nKodi可以運行在多種操作系統和硬件平台。<br />\n它可以讓用戶播放本地或網絡存儲設備中的大多數視頻、音樂、播客及各種常見數字媒體文件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/X_cP9NcXW4NoEf9lYuXzkRdjRT5M17SSgdFnd6hVL0WZ9suQDXbJakZbqysjaRFc1HU=h900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FX_cP9NcXW4NoEf9lYuXzkRdjRT5M17SSgdFnd6hVL0WZ9suQDXbJakZbqysjaRFc1HU%3Dh900&h=e8e4efac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如何安裝Kodi？</strong><br />\n可到官網下載<br />\n<a href=\"https://kodi.tv/download/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkodi.tv%2Fdownload%2F&d=9i0SjJOlFOBs6tAFn2eGcHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=f37eb4bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://kodi.tv/download/</a><br />\nAndroid機亦可到Play Store下載<br />\niOS需要Jailbreak才可安裝<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我應安裝哪個版本？</strong><br />\n現時v17 Krypton仍然開發中，建議安裝穩定版v16.1 Jarvis<br />\n如果想嘗試新功能新介面可下載v17<br />\nv17只支援Android 5.0或以上系統<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Kodi如何設置中文？</strong><br />\n1.進入System -&gt; Settings -&gt; Appearance -&gt; Skin，將其中的Fonts修改成 Arial Based<br />\n2.再進入System -&gt; Settings -&gt; International -&gt; Language，選擇Chinese (Traditional)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Kodi插件系列︰</strong><br />\nExodus<br />\n支援美劇英劇，<a href=\"http://可設置自動下載OpenSubtitles.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%AF%E8%A8%AD%E7%BD%AE%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89OpenSubtitles.org&d=9i0SjJOlFOBs6tAFn2eGcHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1f2a0ddc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">可設置自動下載OpenSubtitles.org</a>中文字幕<br />\n<br />\nIcdrama<br />\n大量TVB劇集，少量日韓台劇。<br />\n<br />\n163sub<br />\n中文字幕plugin。播放影片後到右下角字幕 -&gt; 下載<br />\n<br />\n<strong>安裝方法︰</strong><br />\n1.將滑鼠放在&quot;系統&quot;，選擇檔案總管 -&gt; 新增來源<br />\n上方輸入<br />\n<a href=\"http://fusion.tvaddons.ag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffusion.tvaddons.ag&d=9i0SjJOlFOBs6tAFn2eGcHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7754e074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fusion.tvaddons.ag</a><br />\n下方輸入<br />\nfusion<br />\n2.到&quot;系統設定&quot; -&gt; 附加元件 -&gt; 從zip檔案安裝<br />\n<br />\n安裝Exodus<br />\n1.fusion -&gt; kodi-repos -&gt; english -&gt; repository.exodus-x.x.x.zip<br />\n2.從附加元件庫安裝 -&gt; Exodus repository -&gt; 影片附加元件 -&gt; Exodus<br />\n<br />\n安裝163sub<br />\n1.fusion -&gt; kodi-repos -&gt; international -&gt; chinese-repository.xbmc-addons-x.x.x.zip<br />\n2.從附加元件庫安裝 -&gt; Chinese Add-ons -&gt; 字幕 -&gt; 163sub<br />\n<br />\n安裝Icdrama<br />\n1.檔案總管 -&gt; 新增來源<br />\n<a href=\"https://cthlo.github.io/cthlo-kodi-repo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcthlo.github.io%2Fcthlo-kodi-repo&d=9i0SjJOlFOBs6tAFn2eGcHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=8d946fc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cthlo.github.io/cthlo-kodi-repo</a><br />\n2.&quot;系統設定&quot; -&gt; 附加元件 -&gt; 從zip檔案安裝<br />\ncthlo-kodi-repo -&gt; ./zips -&gt; plugin.video.icdrama -&gt; plugin.video.icdrama-x.x.x.zip<br />\nx.x.x選擇最新版本即可"},{"pid":"60bb23cea7b2d676c7844808223db74f7e80fd6a","tid":87072,"uid":77675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"(自推)"},{"pid":"999acc778f52c4bc5dbef59beb67676add3811cb","tid":87072,"uid":77675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"(自推)"},{"pid":"ada12ab3d748bed890aec56dd54188d62dc7ced0","tid":87072,"uid":60605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:46:42.000Z","msg":"講下我既組合<br />\nandroid tv box <br />\nnas <br />\n通常 download 片落nas <br />\n好少直接用kodi 睇片因為會窒<br />\n<br />\n另外字幕仲有shooter 佢可以自動將簡體字轉繁體字"},{"pid":"ff45d97ee87a5ed5f52d8e0c6deb5080da50b0e6","tid":870